overview.en: YottaChain is a blockchain storage public chain created by Alex Wang, who is one of the top 10 Chinese young scientists. By connecting scatter storage resources globally, YottaChain builds a vast scale storage pool. Its core technology, TruPrivacy, is the only technology realizes de-duplication after encryption in the world. With this global patent technology, YottaChain will surely transform landscape of storage industry.
overview.zh: YottaChain是由中国十大青年科学家王东临带队打造的区块链存储公链，YottaChain通过连接全球分散的存储资源，打造一个规模浩瀚的星际存储池，其核心TruPrivacy技术是全球唯一能实现加密后去重的技术，并荣获全球专利，从而改变存储行业格局。
